op hockey organizations. Experience the speed and skills of higher age players. Develop your release reading.\n\n- Develop you cognitive skills and concentration.", "short_description": "Sense Arena is an off-ice training platform that improves players' Read & React cognitive capabilities, which are critical for peak performance. Our methodology and drills are developed in cooperation with professional NHL players and coaches. The University of Wisconsin-Stevens Point and The Charles University, Prague, have done studies on how players' performances are impacted by using Sense Arena.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.sensearena.com/terms-and-conditions-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.sensearena.com/terms-and-conditions-privacy-policy", "publisher_name": "Sense Arena LLC", "support_website_url": "https://www.sensearena.com/oculus", "website_url": "https://www.sensearena.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "639731507313711"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "CANCELLED", "id": "644973467294216"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "476952649984627"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1559609254848006"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1559609254848006"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1666976400, "status": "CANCELLED", "id": "644973467294216"}]}, "liveChannel": {"no